{"tid":1880432,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"網友直擊：封村引衝突 湖北一村主任被斬首（慎入）","createTime":"2020-02-14T21:40:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-15T12:00:09.000Z","uid":226955,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"2744829fef34ecbacfa3324809db1e84a86531b5","tid":1880432,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T21:40:10.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎失控，多地封城封樓封村之下，民眾生活物資受限，心裡壓力不斷加大，各種意外、慘劇頻發。13日，網上傳出一段視頻，內容指湖北省天門市某村因為封村引發衝突，村主任被斬首，場面血腥。<br />\n<br />\n天門市是湖北省直轄縣級市，曾一度是中共官方數字新冠疫情死亡率最高的城市。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">慎入</span>：<br />\n<a href=\"https://mobile.twitter.com/_Civil_Rights/status/1228002644909625344?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw%7Ctwcamp%5Etweetembed%7Ctwterm%5E1228002644909625344&amp;ref_url=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2F_Civil_Rights%2Fstatus%2F1228002644909625344\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmobile.twitter.com%2F_Civil_Rights%2Fstatus%2F1228002644909625344%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%257Ctwcamp%255Etweetembed%257Ctwterm%255E1228002644909625344%26ref_url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Ftwitter.com%252F_Civil_Rights%252Fstatus%252F1228002644909625344&d=%2BKcr5gC3v3d6Nt4twTTWNvY%2F4yEwT0EAZMYNsJUacQ0%3D&h=b8cac113\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mobile.twitter.com/_Civil_Rights/status/1228002644909625344?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw%7Ctwcamp%5Etweetembed%7Ctwterm%5E1228002644909625344&amp;ref_url=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2F_Civil_Rights%2Fstatus%2F1228002644909625344</a>"},{"pid":"b59dcb0169da78ee575d5fd72b97e27b8c66326d","tid":1880432,"uid":19294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T21:41:57.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"24e755f27de0a7e40ae6ee4c5263e47f032e48c5","tid":1880432,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T21:43:06.000Z","msg":"見到一開始已經血淋淋，搞到我唔敢睇條片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"748ad684526fefe0ab5f2000bfd948f06e639929","tid":1880432,"uid":288670,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"q